snippet.title: Olympian trains with Crossfit Games Athlete for a day | Greg O'Shea
snippet.description:
I got to train with the best Irish Crossfit Games Athlete Sam Stewart for the day and WOW did it humble me. It was such an incredible day and fitness experience. I've been to the Olympics and I thought I was fit until I worked out with this dude!

In the video I do a full day of Crossfit workouts and also interview Sam about how he got to where he is today. I hope you enjoy the video and definitely give Sam a follow on insta (@sam.stewart)

Like, Comment & Subscribe please.

Lots of love,
Greg.
